      "start_time": 15.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "815f43c8-883f-4922-a2a1-1820c2811626",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "um was just looking to speak with someone in regards to marketing and had salt down as the uh the point of contact."
    },
    {
      "id": "992ad5ff-e95e-4b78-97af-d6cce09a3392",
