      "end_time": 54.47,
      "start_time": 34.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": "815f43c8-883f-4922-a2a1-1820c2811626",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "Awesome, awesome. Yeah. Well maybe maybe you could help um just wanted to reach out see how things were going uh in regards to your occupancy. I know it's been some crazy times with everything going on with um and everything there and um you guys are in Kalamazoo, correct?"
