      "recording_id": "2b196c2c-eea8-406b-9c39-8c1db4d16a46",
      "end_time": 82.22,
      "start_time": 56.23,
      "recording_attendee_id": "815f43c8-883f-4922-a2a1-1820c2811626",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "Yeah. So obviously with with some of the universities and things of that nature, I just didn't know how you guys have been affected. We uh we have a partnership with um facebook marketplace and facebook rental ads. I'm sure you guys are on there already. Um but just some of the things that we've been doing and seeing uh have shown really good results in the area. Uh and wanted to touch base."
